text: Karl Münich (born 27 August 1848, date of death unknown) was an Austrian Olympic fencer. He competed in the individual épée event at the 1912 Summer Olympics in Stockholm. ==References== Category:1848 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Austrian male fencers Category:Austrian épée fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Austria Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics
